title: Angela - Asgard's Assassin 005 (2015) (Digital) (Zone-Empire)
description: Superheroic to-do lists are quite the thing. Today, Angela's read 'INVADE MY HOMELAND, WHILST PURSUED BY ASGARDIANS, CARRYING A DEMONIC CHILD WITH ONLY MY SARCASTIC SPACE FRIENDS FOR COMPANY.' What will Starlord do when he discovers that Belinda Carlisle has totally lied to him? BECAUSE HEVEN IS A PLACE FULL OF ANGELS OUT TO KILL HIM. Angela makes a difficult decision. Also some easier ones, primarily involving stabbing
